ZH: 我家的冰箱坏了，需要找人来修理。
EN: The refrigerator in my house is broken and needs to be repaired.

ZH: 请把剩下的食物放进冰箱里保存。
EN: Please put the leftover food in the refrigerator to keep it fresh.

ZH: 我想买一个新的冰箱，这个已经太旧了。
EN: I want to buy a new refrigerator; this one is too old.

ZH: 冰箱里的冰块都融化了。
EN: The ice cubes in the refrigerator have all melted.

ZH: 我把冰箱门关上了，不想让里面的气温升高。
EN: I closed the refrigerator door because I don't want the temperature inside to rise.

ZH: 我刚刚从冰箱里拿了一瓶可乐。
EN: I just took a bottle of cola from the refrigerator.

ZH: 冰箱的温度设置得太低了，食物都结冰了。
EN: The temperature of the refrigerator is set too low; the food has all frozen.

ZH: 妈妈昨天给我买了一盒冰淇淋，我把它放在冰箱里了。
EN: Mom bought me a box of ice cream yesterday, and I put it in the refrigerator.

ZH: 我打开冰箱，发现里面的牛奶都过期了。
EN: I opened the refrigerator and found that all the milk inside has expired.

ZH: 冰箱会发出嗡嗡的声音，好像有东西坏了。
EN: The refrigerator is making a buzzing noise; it seems like something is broken.

ZH: 我把冷冻的食物放进冰箱里去解冻。
EN: I put the frozen food in the refrigerator to thaw.

ZH: 冰箱门被我用胶带修好了，不再漏气了。
EN: I fixed the refrigerator door with tape, so it no longer leaks.

ZH: 冰箱里的食材不够了，需要去超市买一些。
EN: There's not enough food in the refrigerator; I need to go to the supermarket to buy some.

ZH: 我把买的蔬菜放进了冰箱的蔬菜室。
EN: I put the bought vegetables in the refrigerator's vegetable compartment.

ZH: 这个冰箱容量很大，适合家庭使用。
EN: This refrigerator has a large capacity and is suitable for family use.

ZH: 我把从冰箱里拿出来的牛奶倒进了杯子里。
EN: I poured the milk I took out of the refrigerator into a glass.

ZH: 冰箱里的食物都坏了，发出了一股臭味。
EN: The food in the refrigerator has all gone bad and emits a foul smell.

ZH: 我把果汁放进冰箱冷却一下。
EN: I put the juice in the refrigerator to cool it down.

ZH: 这个冰箱定时自动会除霜。
EN: This refrigerator will automatically defrost at regular intervals.

ZH: 冰箱里的东西太多了，都没地方放了。
EN: There's too much stuff in the refrigerator; there's no space left.
